            description="The FilmDescriptor class describes film media.",
            symbol="FilmDescriptor")
public class FilmDescriptorImpl
extends EssenceDescriptorImpl
implements FilmDescriptor, Serializable, Cloneable

    Implements the description of film media. A SourcePackage described by a film descriptor is known as a film source package.
